ts.name: ts
ts.description: Timestamp for the recorded RSI data.

o.name: o
o.description: Opening price of the asset at the given timestamp.

c.name: c
c.description: Closing price of the asset at the given timestamp.

h.name: h
h.description: Highest price reached within the given timestamp.

l.name: l
l.description: Lowest price reached within the given timestamp.

v.name: v
v.description: Trading volume of the asset for the given timestamp.

vwap.name: vwap
vwap.description: Volume Weighted Average Price (VWAP) for the asset during the given period.

rsi.name: rsi
rsi.description: Relative Strength Index (RSI), a momentum oscillator that measures the speed and change of price movements.

td_buy_count.name: td_buy_count
td_buy_count.description: Number of consecutive bullish TD Sequential buy signals.

td_sell_count.name: td_sell_count
td_sell_count.description: Number of consecutive bearish TD Sequential sell signals.

macd_curvature.name: macd_curvature
macd_curvature.description: Current trend of the MACD (e.g., upward, downward, neutral).

timespan.name: timespan
timespan.description: The timespan of the data point (e.g., 1min, 5min, 1h, 1d).

ticker.name: ticker
ticker.description: Stock ticker symbol associated with the RSI data.

insertion_timestamp.name: insertion_timestamp
insertion_timestamp.description: Timestamp when this RSI data was inserted into the database.

bullish_engulfing.name: bullish_engulfing
bullish_engulfing.description: Boolean flag indicating if a bullish engulfing candlestick pattern has formed.

bearish_engulfing.name: bearish_engulfing
bearish_engulfing.description: Boolean flag indicating if a bearish engulfing candlestick pattern has formed.

middle_band.name: middle_band
middle_band.description: The middle band of a Bollinger Band, calculated as the moving average.

upper_band.name: upper_band
upper_band.description: The upper Bollinger Band, calculated as moving average + (standard deviation * multiplier).

lower_band.name: lower_band
lower_band.description: The lower Bollinger Band, calculated as moving average - (standard deviation * multiplier).

upper_bb_trend.name: upper_bb_trend
upper_bb_trend.description: Current trend of the upper Bollinger Band (e.g., expanding, contracting).

lower_bb_trend.name: lower_bb_trend
lower_bb_trend.description: Current trend of the lower Bollinger Band (e.g., expanding, contracting).

candle_above_upper.name: candle_above_upper
candle_above_upper.description: Boolean flag indicating if the entire candlestick is above the upper Bollinger Band.

candle_below_lower.name: candle_below_lower
candle_below_lower.description: Boolean flag indicating if the entire candlestick is below the lower Bollinger Band.

at_upper_band.name: at_upper_band
at_upper_band.description: Boolean flag indicating if the price is touching the upper Bollinger Band.

obv.name: obv
obv.description: On-Balance Volume (OBV) indicator, which tracks cumulative volume based on price direction.

candle_completely_above_upper.name: candle_completely_above_upper
candle_completely_above_upper.description: Boolean flag indicating if the entire candle body and wicks are above the upper Bollinger Band.

candle_completely_below_lower.name: candle_completely_below_lower
candle_completely_below_lower.description: Boolean flag indicating if the entire candle body and wicks are below the lower Bollinger Band.

candle_partially_below_lower.name: candle_partially_below_lower
candle_partially_below_lower.description: Boolean flag indicating if part of the candle body or wick is below the lower Bollinger Band.

candle_partially_above_upper.name: candle_partially_above_upper
candle_partially_above_upper.description: Boolean flag indicating if part of the candle body or wick is above the upper Bollinger Band.

volume_diff.name: volume_diff
volume_diff.description: The difference in volume compared to the previous period.

volume_pct_change.name: volume_pct_change
volume_pct_change.description: The percentage change in volume compared to the previous period.

volume_increasing_streak.name: volume_increasing_streak
volume_increasing_streak.description: The number of consecutive periods with increasing volume.

volume_decreasing_streak.name: volume_decreasing_streak
volume_decreasing_streak.description: The number of consecutive periods with decreasing volume.

body_completely_above_upper.name: body_completely_above_upper
body_completely_above_upper.description: Boolean flag indicating if the entire candle body is above the upper Bollinger Band.

body_completely_below_lower.name: body_completely_below_lower
body_completely_below_lower.description: Boolean flag indicating if the entire candle body is below the lower Bollinger Band.
